item.title: ICSM conquer IC in LUSL Vase
item.author: Michael David,
item.description: Following talk of an unbeaten season following three wins from three games at the start of the season, the ICSM FC 2nd XI had taken a nose dive. A string of losses left Captain Ali Brown and his men dejected and in desperate need of a win. A quarter final tie against rivals, IC 5th XI, in the LUSL â€¦
